T02TD1445E:272b-1: shr'i tsakra sam ba ra s'a dha nam n'a ma /
T02TD1445E:272b-3: dpal 'khor lo sdom pa zhes bya ba'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD1445E:272b-4: bcom ldan 'das dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1445E:272b-5: yi dgas gdan la bzhugs shing zhal rnams kun la spyan gsum dang ni phag mo dmar mo'i lus //
T02TD1445E:272b-6: rtsa ba'i phyag gnyis kyis 'khyud gzhan gnyis kyis ni myur du glang chen gtso bo'i pags pa brgyangs //
T02TD1445E:272b-7: lhag ma g-yon pa'i phyag bzhis kha tv'am ga dang zhags pa mi thod tshangs pa'i mgo bo 'phyang //
T02TD1445E:272b-8: g-yas pas gri gug rtse gsum dgra sta rnge'u chung 'chang ba'i he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1445E:272b-9: bde mchog 'khor lo gsang ba'i don //
T02TD1445E:272b-10: sgrub pa'i gsang sngags kun bsdus nas //
T02TD1445E:272b-11: brda yi skad kyis sbas pas te //
T02TD1445E:272b-12: sgrub pa'i thabs de bdag gis bshad //
T02TD1445E:272b-13: snying ga'i sa bon 'od chogs kyis //
T02TD1445E:272b-14: mdun du bde gshegs spyan drangs nas //
T02TD1445E:272b-15: mchod pa kun gyis legs mchod de //
T02TD1445E:272b-16: dkon mchog gsum la sogs pa brjod //
T02TD1445E:272b-17: thams cad stong par rnam bsgoms nas //
T02TD1445E:272b-18: sna tshogs pad nyi h'um rdo rje //
T02TD1445E:272b-20: blo dang ldan pas phur sogs bya ;
T02TD1445E:272b-21: / blo dang ldan pas mkha' dbyings su //
T02TD1445E:272b-23: ji ltar sna tshogs bzhir gyur pa'i //
T02TD1445E:272b-24: 'byung ba bzhi yi rnam pa bsgom //
T02TD1445E:272b-25: de yi rim pa 'di yin te //
T02TD1445E:272b-26: ba lang gnas kyi lci skam dang //
T02TD1445E:272b-27: lhag ma mgo skam de nas su //
T02TD1445E:273a-2: mi phyed rus sbal dag 'gyur bas //
T02TD1445E:273a-3: phyag bzhi pa dang zhabs bzhi pa //
T02TD1445E:273a-4: de bzhin phyag 'bum bar du ste //
T02TD1445E:273a-5: sku mdog dkar po khro bo che //
T02TD1445E:273a-6: rdo rje dril bu lus la 'khyud //
T02TD1445E:273a-7: dpa' bo thod pa'i phreng ba can //
T02TD1445E:273a-8: sku la thal bas nye bar byugs //
T02TD1445E:273a-9: zhal gyi mtshe ba cung zad gtsigs //
T02TD1445E:273a-10: yi dags chen po gdan du byas //
T02TD1445E:273a-11: rgyal ba'i 'od zer sprin chen po //
T02TD1445E:273a-12: de las kun du rnam par 'phro //
T02TD1445E:273a-13: phyag rgya drug gis lus la brgyan //
T02TD1445E:273a-14: ral pa yi ni thor tshugs can //
T02TD1445E:273a-15: g-yas kyi zhal ni gang pa ste //
T02TD1445E:273a-16: g-yon pa dmar pa 'jigs pa can //
T02TD1445E:273a-17: rtsa ba'i zhal ni shin tu dkar //
T02TD1445E:273a-18: rgyab ni gser du snang ba'o //
T02TD1445E:273a-19: dus min 'chi las rnam rgyal zhing //
T02TD1445E:273a-20: yan lag kha tv'am ga dang sbyar //
T02TD1445E:273a-21: thod pa aargha snod kyis ni //
T02TD1445E:273a-22: zhal dang mtshon char nges sbyar ba'o //
T02TD1445E:273a-23: de yi shes rab 'jigs pa ma //
T02TD1445E:273a-24: thod pa'i dum bu'i ske rags can //
T02TD1445E:273a-25: thod pa shin tu gang ba dang //
T02TD1445E:273a-26: de yi kha dog lag char 'dzin //
T02TD1445E:273a-27: ri bo tshang tshing sman ljongs dang //
T02TD1445E:273a-28: rgya mtsho chen po'i ngos dag la //
T02TD1445E:273a-29: gdod nas grub pa'i dur khrod du //
T02TD1445E:273a-30: der ni dkyil 'khor bri bar bya //
T02TD1445E:273a-31: ji ltar chos kyi skur gyur pa'o //
T02TD1445E:273a-32: de ltar sprul dang bsrung par bya //
T02TD1445E:273a-33: kha sbyor kha sbyor du gyur pa //
T02TD1445E:273a-34: rdo rje lu gu rgyud du brjod //
T02TD1445E:273a-36: de tshe bud ba lta bur 'khor //
T02TD1445E:273a-37: brud pa rdo rje nyid du bshad //
T02TD1445E:273a-38: de nas rim bzhin spros byas nas //
T02TD1445E:273a-39: lcags kyu nyid kyis 'khyud bya ste //
T02TD1445E:273a-40: gtun shing gis ni bskyod par bya //
T02TD1445E:273a-41: dbyig pa'i mda' yis mnyam sgyor te ;
T02TD1445E:273a-42: / de nas rig ma zhu bar gyur //
T02TD1445E:273a-43: sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa yi //
T02TD1445E:273a-44: myur ba nyid du bdag la bskul //
T02TD1445E:273a-45: aom ma h'a su kha badzra satva dza: h'um bam ho: su ra ta stvam dri shya ho //
T02TD1445E:273a-46: yongs su bskul ba tsam gyis ni //
T02TD1445E:273a-47: 'jig rten khams kyi bde ba'i bdag / ji ltar bskyed pa'i rim pa bzhin ;
T02TD1445E:273a-48: / gnyug ma'i sngags las byung gyur te //
T02TD1445E:273a-49: khu ba'i gzugs las rdo rje can //
T02TD1445E:273a-50: de nas aam h'um gnyis las bzhengs //
T02TD1445E:273a-51: kha dog sngon po 'jigs pa po //
T02TD1445E:273a-53: zhal bzhi pa ste 'jogs pa can //
T02TD1445E:273b-0: drug gnyis phyag gis rnam @273b par brgyan //
T02TD1445E:273b-1: au ma au ma'i bdag po mnan //
T02TD1445E:273b-2: nyin byed dbang phyug gdan du bting //
T02TD1445E:273b-3: rtsa ba'i zhal ni shin tu gang / g-yas pa kunda lta bu ste //
T02TD1445E:273b-4: g-yon pa dmar po 'jigs pa po //
T02TD1445E:273b-6: sngar gyi lag char yang dag ldan //
T02TD1445E:273b-7: spyan gsum gyis kyang yang dag mdzes //
T02TD1445E:273b-8: cung zad khro zhing bzhad pa'i zhal //
T02TD1445E:273b-9: g-yon brkyang ba yi gar gyis bzhugs //
T02TD1445E:273b-10: de yi shes rab phag mo ni //
T02TD1445E:273b-11: dmar mo kha dog cher 'bar ba //
T02TD1445E:273b-12: zhal gcig phyag gnyis rnam par mdzes //
T02TD1445E:273b-13: rdo rje dang ni mi thod 'phyang //
T02TD1445E:273b-14: bcom ldan 'das kyis zhal bzhi byin gyis brlab pa ni //
T02TD1445E:273b-15: aom sumbha ni sumbha h'um h'um phat //
T02TD1445E:273b-16: aom grihna grihna h'um h'um phat /
T02TD1445E:273b-17: aom gridn'a pa ya grihn'a pa ya h'um h'um phat /
T02TD1445E:273b-18: aom a'a na ya ho bha ga b'an bidy'a r'a dza h'um h'um phat /
T02TD1445E:273b-19: de ni lugs las bzlas pa'o //
T02TD1445E:273b-20: aom dharm'a dh'a tu sva bh'a ba a'atma ko& ham zhes bya ba ni bsnyen pa'o //
T02TD1445E:273b-21: aom ha snying gar rdo rje sems dpa' 'o //
T02TD1445E:273b-22: aom na ma hi spyi bor rnam par snang mdzad do //
T02TD1445E:273b-23: aom sv'a h'a hu spyi gtsug tu padma gar gyi dbang phyug go //
T02TD1445E:273b-24: aom boo sha ta he mchan khung gnyis su dpal he ru ka'o //
T02TD1445E:273b-25: aom h'um h'um ho mig gnyis su rdo rje nyi ma'o //
T02TD1445E:273b-26: aom phat ham rta mgrin te /
T02TD1445E:273b-27: yan lag thams cad la mtshon cha'o //
T02TD1445E:273b-28: aom aom bam lte bar rdo rje phag mo'o //
T02TD1445E:273b-29: aom ham yom snying gar gshin rje ma'o //
T02TD1445E:273b-30: aom hrim mom khar rmongs byed ma'o //
T02TD1445E:273b-31: aom hrem hrim spyi bor skyod byed ma'o //
T02TD1445E:273b-32: aom h'um h'um spyi gtsug tu skrag byed ma'o //
T02TD1445E:273b-33: aom phat phat lha mo'i gnas thams cad la /
T02TD1445E:273b-35: / snying ga'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la gnas pa'i yi ge h'um ni thugs rdo rje'o //
T02TD1445E:273b-36: aom hr'i: ha ha h'um h'um phat lkog mar gsung rdo rje'o //
T02TD1445E:273b-37: aom shr'i badzra he he ru ru kam h'um h'um phat d'a ki n'i dz'a la sam ba ra sv'a h'a ni dpral bar sku rdo rje'o //
T02TD1445E:273b-38: aom sarbba bu ddha d'a ki n'i ye badzra wa rna n'i ye h'um h'um phat sv'a h'a zhes bya ba ni lha mo'i snying gar ro //
T02TD1445E:273b-39: aom tsa ham h'um phat lkog mar ro //
T02TD1445E:273b-40: aom badzra bee ro tsa ni h'um phat dpral bar ro //
T02TD1445E:273b-41: spyi bor yi ge aom mo //
T02TD1445E:273b-42: snying gar yi ge h'um ngo //
T02TD1445E:273b-43: ze 'bru la ni yi ge a'a:'o //
T02TD1445E:273b-44: rked par ni yi ge sv'a'o //
T02TD1445E:273b-45: brlar ni yi ge h'a'o zhes bya ba ni sgrub pa'o //
T02TD1445E:274a-2: de phyir 'di ni rdo rjer brjod //
T02TD1445E:274a-3: dbang gi don ni bsgoms byas nas //
T02TD1445E:274a-4: phyis ni mchod pas mnyes par bya //
T02TD1445E:274a-5: lingga gnyis la sngags bkod la //
T02TD1445E:274a-6: sna rtser aa yig rnam par dgod //
T02TD1445E:274a-7: de bzhin lingga'i lte ba la //
T02TD1445E:274a-8: yi ge bam ni rnam par bsam ;
T02TD1445E:274a-9: / blo ldan rnal 'byor ma la bsrub //
T02TD1445E:274a-10: dag pa'i lus ni dri ma med //
T02TD1445E:274a-11: ces bya ba 'di ni dang po'i rnal 'byor ro //
T02TD1445E:274a-12: aom sarbba ta th'a ga ta aa nu r'a ga na a'atma ko& ham //
T02TD1445E:274a-13: snying ga'i sa bon 'od zer gyis //
T02TD1445E:274a-14: bde bar gshegs pa spyan drangs te //
T02TD1445E:274a-15: aa wa dh'u t'i gnas de bzhin //
T02TD1445E:274a-16: smin ma'i bar du nges par gzhug / dang por dbyangs dang yang dag ldan //
T02TD1445E:274a-17: de ni skad cig gis gsal bsgom //
T02TD1445E:274a-18: mgal me'i 'khor lo ltar gnas pa //
T02TD1445E:274a-19: rnal 'byor ma ni de bzhin no //
T02TD1445E:274a-20: 'bar ba'i phreng ba du ma ni //
T02TD1445E:274a-21: 'khor lo thams cad kyi ni sgo //
T02TD1445E:274a-22: zhal bzhi dpa' bo rnams kyis so //
T02TD1445E:274a-23: dpa' bo rnal 'byor mas yongs bskor //
T02TD1445E:274a-24: rtsa ba'i lam ni thams cad du //
T02TD1445E:274a-25: sngags pa ji ltar dbye 'dod pas //
T02TD1445E:274a-26: de nyid dbye ba tha dad nyid //
T02TD1445E:274a-27: mkha' 'gro ma ni nyis sbyor byed //
T02TD1445E:274a-28: chags pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor ni //
T02TD1445E:274a-29: dgos pa'i phyir ni rab sgrub byed //
T02TD1445E:274a-30: dam ba'i rnal 'byor ma rnams kun //
T02TD1445E:274a-31: yul dang yul la nges par sbyar //
T02TD1445E:274a-32: de nas mkha' 'gro ma rnams ni //
T02TD1445E:274a-33: gnas la rnam par gnas pa ste //
T02TD1445E:274a-34: shar nas mkha' 'gro ma sngo skya'i 'od can no //
T02TD1445E:274a-35: byang nas l'a ma ljang ser ma'o //
T02TD1445E:274a-36: nub nas dum skyes ma dmar ser ro //
T02TD1445E:274a-37: lho nas gzugs can ma dkar ser gyi mdog can te /
T02TD1445E:274a-38: 'di thams cad ni ro'i steng na thod pa dang gri gug lag na thogs pa /
T02TD1445E:274a-40: rgyan rnams kyis brgyan pa zhal gcig pa /
T02TD1445E:274a-41: dbu la sangs rgyas kyi gzugs brnyan gyis mtshan cing yang dag par ldan par gar stabs kyis bzhugs pa'o //
T02TD1445E:274a-42: thod pa rnams su glang po dang ce spyang dang mi dang ba lang rnams rim pa ji lta ba'o //
T02TD1445E:274a-43: mtshams bzhir yang lngar gcig gis ma tshang ba'i snod do //
T02TD1445E:274a-44: mgo bo pulli ra ma la ya nas khanda ka p'a li dang rab tu gtum mo ste //
T02TD1445E:274b-0: @274b spyi gtsug 'bar ba 'dzin pa nas ma h'a kam ka la dang gtum pa'i mig can ma ste /
T02TD1445E:274b-2: rna ba g-yas pa au dya na nas kam ka la dang 'od ldan ma ste /
T02TD1445E:274b-3: pags pa dang dri ma 'bab pa'o //
T02TD1445E:274b-4: ltag pa aarbu da nas mche ba rnam par gtsigs pa dang /
T02TD1445E:274b-5: sna chen ma ste sha 'bab pa'o //
T02TD1445E:274b-6: de dag ni shar phyogs la sogs pa nas lugs dang mthun pa'o //
T02TD1445E:274b-7: rna ba g-yon pa'i mchod sbyin nas dpa' bo bzang po dang /
T02TD1445E:274b-9: thams cad du chu rgyus 'bab pa'o //
T02TD1445E:274b-10: smin dbus dga' ba'i dbang phyug nas 'od dpag tu med pa dang ;
T02TD1445E:274b-12: rus pa dang dri ma 'bab pa'o //
T02TD1445E:274b-13: mig gnyis lha mo'i mkhar nas rdo rje 'od dang langka'i dbang phyug ma ste /
T02TD1445E:274b-14: de ni rtag tu mchi ma 'bab pa'o //
T02TD1445E:274b-15: dpung pa m'a la be nas rdo rje'i lus dang /
T02TD1445E:274b-16: shing grib ma ste snying ga'i chu ba 'bab pa'o //
T02TD1445E:274b-17: de dag ni dbang ldan la sogs pa'i mtshams nas /
T02TD1445E:274b-18: thugs kyi 'khor lo'i mkha' spyod ma rnams snyoms par zhugs pas bzhugs so //
T02TD1445E:274b-19: de bzhin du mchan khung 'dod pa'i gzugs nas aam gu ri dang /
T02TD1445E:274b-22: nu ma gnyis po ao tre nas /
T02TD1445E:274b-23: rdo rje ral pa can dang /
T02TD1445E:274b-26: lte ba tri sha ku ne nas dpa' bo chen po dang /
T02TD1445E:274b-27: rlung gi shugs can ma ste /
T02TD1445E:274b-29: sna'i rtse mo ko sa la nas /
T02TD1445E:274b-30: badzra h'um ka ra dang chang 'thung ma ste /
T02TD1445E:274b-32: de dag ni shar la sogs pa nas so //
T02TD1445E:274b-33: kha ka lingga nas su bha dra dang /
T02TD1445E:274b-35: logs kyi rtsa 'bab par bshad pa'o //
T02TD1445E:274b-36: mgrin pa lam p'a ka nas rdo rje bzang po dang /
T02TD1445E:274b-39: snying k'anytsi nas 'jigs byed chen mo dang /
T02TD1445E:274b-42: mdoms par hi m'a la nas mig mi bzang dang /
T02TD1445E:274b-46: gsung gi 'khor los spyod ma ste /
T02TD1445E:274b-47: de rnams ni snyoms par zhugs pas rnam par gnas so //
T02TD1445E:274b-48: lingga yi dags gnas pa nas //
T02TD1445E:274b-49: stobs po che dang 'khor lo'i shugs can te //
T02TD1445E:275a-2: bshang ba'i lam khyim gyi gnas nas rin chen rdo rje dang /
T02TD1445E:275a-3: dum skyes ma ste dri ni rtag tu 'bab pa'o //
T02TD1445E:275a-5: rta mgrin dang chang 'tshong ma ste /
T02TD1445E:275a-6: khrag 'bab par rab tu grags pa'o //
T02TD1445E:275a-7: byin pa gnyis gser gling nas /
T02TD1445E:275a-11: de dag ni shar la sogs pa'i phyogs so //
T02TD1445E:275a-12: sor mo na ga ra nas ni dpal he ru ka dang /
T02TD1445E:275a-15: rkang pa'i rgya ba sindhu nas ni padma gar gyi dbang phyug dang stobs chen mo ste /
T02TD1445E:275a-16: 'di ni rtag tu mchi ma 'bab pa'o //
T02TD1445E:275a-17: mthe bo mya ngam nas rnam par snang mdzad dang 'khor los sgyur ma ste /
T02TD1445E:275a-19: pus mo ku lu t'a nas /
T02TD1445E:275a-20: rdo rje sems dpa' dang brtson 'grus chen mo ste /
T02TD1445E:275a-22: sngon bzhin mtshams rnams su ste /
T02TD1445E:275a-23: sku'i 'khor los 'og na spyod pa rnams snyoms par zhugs pas bzhugs so //
T02TD1445E:275a-24: shar gyi sgo nas khva gdong ma'o //
T02TD1445E:275a-27: lho phyogs nas phag gdong can te /
T02TD1445E:275a-28: mkha' 'gro ma la sogs pa rnams kyi kha dog dang mtshan ma dang ldan pa /
T02TD1445E:275a-29: ro la zhon cing de las 'od zer 'bar bas /
T02TD1445E:275a-30: bzhin kun du rnam par 'gyur zhing sna tshogs su rnam pa bsgyur ba ste /
T02TD1445E:275a-32: pho nya mo rnams ni lugs dang mi mthun pas yang dag par rnam par gzhag ste /
T02TD1445E:275a-33: me'i mtshams nas gshin rje pho nya mo'o //
T02TD1445E:275a-34: srin po'i mtshams nas gshen rje brtan ma'o //
T02TD1445E:275a-36: gshin rje mche ba gtsigs ma'o //
T02TD1445E:275a-37: dbang ldan gyi mtshams nas gshin rje 'dzoms ma ste /
T02TD1445E:275a-38: 'di dag kyang kha dog nyis gnyis ma'o //
T02TD1445E:275a-39: yid du 'ong ma lnga ma lta bur ro la zhon pa'o //
T02TD1445E:275a-40: dpal he ru ka la sogs pa dpa' bo rnams ni rdo rje dang dril bus 'khyud pa'i phyag rgya can no //
T02TD1445E:275a-41: lha mo thams cad kyi phyag na gri gug dang thod pa thogs pa sgeg pa la sogs pa'i nyams dang ldan pa /
T02TD1445E:275a-42: spyan gsum ma mche ba gtsigs pa /
T02TD1445E:275a-43: thod pa'i phreng bas brgyan pa /
T02TD1445E:275a-44: 'od zer du ma spro zhing 'bar pa /
T02TD1445E:275b-0: khro gnyer yon po'i mig gis @275b blta ba ;
T02TD1445E:275b-1: ro mnan cing de las 'od zer 'bar ba /
T02TD1445E:275b-2: nyi ma la gar gyis bzhugs pa'o //
T02TD1445E:275b-3: khva'i gdong can ma la sogs pa bshad pa ni /
T02TD1445E:275b-4: stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs can //
T02TD1445E:275b-5: thor tshugs kyi nor bu dang //
T02TD1445E:275b-6: rna cha dang mgul rgyan dang /
T02TD1445E:275b-7: gdu bu dang rdo rje'i rked pa dang /
T02TD1445E:275b-8: thod pa'i phreng bas mgul pa brgyan pa /
T02TD1445E:275b-9: de bzhin du rkang pa gnyis la dril bu g-yer khas brgyan pa /
T02TD1445E:275b-10: shin tu g-yon brkyang bas bzhugs pa'o //
T02TD1445E:275b-11: gong gi dpa' bo nyi shu bzhi //
T02TD1445E:275b-12: he ru ka dpal rigs byung pa //
T02TD1445E:275b-13: mkha' 'gro ma ni nyi shu bzhi //
T02TD1445E:275b-14: phag mo'i rigs las byung ba'o //
T02TD1445E:275b-15: ye shes dam tshig mnyam gyur pas //
T02TD1445E:275b-16: de phyir rdo rje zhes su brjod //
T02TD1445E:275b-17: dbang gi don ni bsgom byas nas //
T02TD1445E:275b-18: phyi nang mchod pas mnyes byas te //
T02TD1445E:275b-19: thams cad snga ma lta bu'o //
T02TD1445E:275b-20: da ni byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun gyi lha'i sbyor bas rnam par gzhag ste /
T02TD1445E:275b-21: lus dran pa nye bar gzhag pa ni /
T02TD1445E:275b-22: mkha' 'gro ma zhes bya ba nas /
T02TD1445E:275b-23: mi dge ba'i chos ma skyes pa rnams mi bskyed pa ni gshin rje brtan ma'o zhes bya ba'i bar /
T02TD1445E:275b-24: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje 'chang chen pos gsungs te /
T02TD1445E:275b-25: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun gyi lha'i rnam par dag pa'o //
T02TD1445E:275b-26: snying gi nang song padma ni //
T02TD1445E:275b-27: 'dab ma brgyad pa ge sar bcas //
T02TD1445E:275b-28: de yi nang du son pa'i rtsa //
T02TD1445E:275b-29: mar me lta bu'i rang bzhin te //
T02TD1445E:275b-30: chu shing gi ni me tog bzhin //
T02TD1445E:275b-32: de yi nang song dpa' bo ni //
T02TD1445E:275b-33: yungs kar sbom phra'i tshad tsam ste //
T02TD1445E:275b-34: gzhom med h'um ste sa bon ni //
T02TD1445E:275b-35: ba mo lta bur 'dzag pa nyid ;
T02TD1445E:275b-36: / lus can rnams kyi snying dga' ba //
T02TD1445E:275b-37: de phyir zhes bya rnam par bshad //
T02TD1445E:275b-38: me ni chen po'i gzugs kyis ni //
T02TD1445E:275b-39: phag mo'i thig le ru ni brjod //
T02TD1445E:275b-40: las kyi rlung gis bskul ba yis //
T02TD1445E:275b-42: dpyid thob pas ni mnyes gyur nas /
T02TD1445E:275b-43: snyoms par 'jug pa rnam par gnas //
T02TD1445E:275b-44: 'di ni he ru ka dpal dpa' //
T02TD1445E:275b-45: dpyid kyi thig ler brjod ba'o //
T02TD1445E:275b-46: stong pa nyid kyi tshul 'dzin ma //
T02TD1445E:275b-47: rgyu dang mi rgyu yang dag gnas //
T02TD1445E:275b-48: sku gsung thugs kyi dbye ba yis //
T02TD1445E:275b-49: sgo ni rnam pa gsum 'byung bar //
T02TD1445E:276a-0: @276a * // 'di dag thams cad lus la gnas //
T02TD1445E:276a-1: lte ba'i aa yi tshul gyis ni //
T02TD1445E:276a-2: thung du ru ni yongs su grags //
T02TD1445E:276a-3: snying la h'um gi yi ge ni //
T02TD1445E:276a-4: ring po tshad gnyis dag tu gnas //
T02TD1445E:276a-5: mgrin par aom gyi gzugs kyi ni //
T02TD1445E:276a-6: shin tu ring po tshad gsum pas //
T02TD1445E:276a-7: dpral ba'i ham zhes bya ba ni //
T02TD1445E:276a-8: mi shigs pa yi thig le'o //
T02TD1445E:276a-9: 'khor lo bzhi yi dbye ba yis //
T02TD1445E:276a-10: sa sogs 'byung ba bzhi dag dang //
T02TD1445E:276a-11: thun bzhis byin gyis brlabs pa yis //
T02TD1445E:276a-12: skad cig bzhi ni 'byung ba dang //
T02TD1445E:276a-13: dga' ba bzhi yi rang bzhin gyis //
T02TD1445E:276a-14: sbyor ba bzhi ni sngon du'o //
T02TD1445E:276a-15: mchog tu dga' ba'i mtshan nyid kyis //
T02TD1445E:276a-16: bya dang byed pa'i dngos po min //
T02TD1445E:276a-17: rdo rje sems dpa'i tshul gyis ni //
T02TD1445E:276a-18: 'dir ni ji ltar bde bar rol //
T02TD1445E:276a-20: phyogs bzhir rnam par gnas pa ni //
T02TD1445E:276a-21: 'byung ba bzhi yi rtsa yin te //
T02TD1445E:276a-22: mar me lta bu'i rang bzhin no //
T02TD1445E:276a-23: mtshams su rnam par gnas pa'i tshe //
T02TD1445E:276a-24: de ni nang sor bzhi po yang //
T02TD1445E:276a-25: de nas bdud rtsi lnga 'bab pa //
T02TD1445E:276a-26: de nyid rang bzhin med tshul gyi //
T02TD1445E:276a-27: 'dir ni mchod pa'i tshul gnas pas //
T02TD1445E:276a-28: mchod pa bzhin du yang dag bshad //
T02TD1445E:276a-29: lus kyi snying gi nang na ni //
T02TD1445E:276a-30: rtsa rnams brgyad ni rnam par gnas /
T02TD1445E:276a-31: gzhan yang sku gsung thugs dbye bas //
T02TD1445E:276a-32: nyi shu rtsa bzhi yang dag bshad //
T02TD1445E:276a-33: gnas sogs dbye ba la brten te //
T02TD1445E:276a-34: gnas dang gnas la rnam par gnas //
T02TD1445E:276a-35: ltung byed la sogs rnam dag pa //
T02TD1445E:276a-36: khva gdong la sogs sngar ji bzhin //
T02TD1445E:276a-37: zhes bcom ldan 'das rdo rje can gyis rgyas btab pa'i phyir gsungs so //
T02TD1445E:276a-38: rdzas bcu las ni sngar bsam pa //
T02TD1445E:276a-39: yi ge aa las byung ba'i snod //
T02TD1445E:276a-40: rlung gi me yi dkyil 'khor la //
T02TD1445E:276a-41: sbar bas kho la bar gyur pa dang //
T02TD1445E:276a-42: dbyangs yi ga dang po yang dag ldan //
T02TD1445E:276a-43: skad cig de las 'bar zhing blta //
T02TD1445E:276a-44: bzlog pa'i yi ge mnyam sbyor ba //
T02TD1445E:276a-45: rgyud kyi sngags ni bsgom par bya //
T02TD1445E:276a-46: yi ge aom gyis kun gsal bas //
T02TD1445E:276a-47: de nyid gsum la yang dag brjod //
T02TD1445E:276a-48: de ltar bsgoms gyur na lha mo //
T02TD1445E:276a-49: rdzas kyi dngos grub bzang po byed //
T02TD1445E:276b-0: byin gyis brlabs par @276b yang dag 'gyur /
T02TD1445E:276b-1: aom a'a ralli dza: h'um bam ho: sa ma ya stvam /
T02TD1445E:276b-3: kha kha kh'a hi kh'a hi /

T02TD1445E:276b-5: aom na mo bha ga wa te b'i re sh'a ya /

T02TD1445E:276b-25: a'a kaddhya a'a kaddhya hrim hrim dznyoom dznyoom /
T02TD1445E:276b-34: sngags thams cad kyi mtha' ru h'um dang phat ces bya ba'i yi ge sbyar ro //

T02TD1445E:276b-56: phat ham dpa' po'i go cha drug go //
